<section sectnbr = "8B">
<servcat sctnbr = "08" scnbr = "02">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENCP70A8206003" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
SDM Removal and Installation
</title>
<attention1>
<ptxt>
During service procedures, be careful when handling a SDM.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Be sure to read 
<intxref refid = "AENCP70A8200002">Precautions for Handling and Storage of Air Bag System Components</intxref>
 before starting to work and observe every precaution during work. Neglecting them may result in personal injury, death or inactivation of air bag system when necessary.
</ptxt>
</attention1>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A8206003001">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disable air bag system. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A8206001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove floor console rear box. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9806013"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Turn over floor carpet. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9806010"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove bolts (1), then remove bracket (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A820048.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "76.877mm" ver = "01" gw = "234" gh = "201"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect SDM connectors (1).
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove SDM bolts (2), then remove SDM (3).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A820046.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "68.795mm" ver = "01" gw = "236" gh = "178"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A8206003002">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENCP70A8206004">SDM Inspection</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Reverse removal procedure noting the following points.
</ptxt>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check that none of the following faulty conditions exists.
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Bend, scratch, deformity on mating surface of vehicle body where SDM is mounted.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Foreign matter or rust on mating surface of vehicle body where SDM is mounted.
</ptxt>
</s2>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Ensure that arrow (1) on SDM is pointing toward front of vehicle.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Tighten SDM bolts (2) to specified torque.
</ptxt>
<torque>
<torqueitem id = "T8B001">
<t-part>
SDM bolt
</t-part>
<t-part1>
a
</t-part1>
<t-value1>
9.0
</t-value1>
<t-value2>
0.92
</t-value2>
<t-value3>
7.0
</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A820047.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "70.496mm" ver = "01" gw = "236" gh = "183"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install bracket (2), then tighten bolts (1).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A820049.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "76.877mm" ver = "01" gw = "234" gh = "201"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Enable air bag system. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A8206002"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
</section></manual></suzuki>
